node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Brandon Tatum 🇺🇸 in Union Station. May be an image of 1 person, beard, standing and outdoors.

node.text:
Caption this!!

*I stopped and spoke with them, because they just knew I was going to be anti police and worshiping the "White Privilege" god and his goddess "Systemic Racism". They had the wrong guy!! It's funny how white liberals try to tell a black man how oppressed I am.

I should add. They were very respectful and so was I.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Brandon Tatum 🇺🇸 in MLB All-Star Game. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and text.

node.text: People keep asking me, "Why do you support the MLB". I don't support the MLB. I support my Son who couldn't care less about the MLB and VOTING in Georgia. He love baseball and I'm going to give him all the opportunities I never had. So, take a chill pill!!

node.text: This young man really admired me. I likewise admired him. He was Dressed nice and well behaved. I brought him back to the green room and showed him love.
